eneralization from superficial pattern matching. If models fail despite high accuracy on standard benchmarks, it reveals a critical gap in systematic reasoning. Conversely, success would provide strong evidence for compositional understanding of logical semantics in LLMs. The broader impact includes a new evaluation paradigm for assessing deep linguistic competence in AI systems, with implications for developing more logically coherent and trustworthy language technologies.",
